    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that's a pretty blunt way to put it lol. so you're saying it's basically just a talk shop? do historians see the whole idea of a \"global security framework\" as a real possibility, or is that just something people say when they want to ignore how much countries actually care about their own sovereignty?",
